window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Harper McKenzie wakes to the worse possible day: her 18-year-old son has vanished from her Manhattan apartment without trace.</p> <p>Worse, no-one knows what she’s talking about.&nbsp;</p> <p>No-one thinks she had a son.&nbsp;</p> <p>Ever.</p> <p>Has she lost her grip on reality?</p> <p>Or has the world shifted in a terrifying and unpredictable way?</p> <p><i>The Effect</i> is a taut psychological thriller that challenges everything we thought was real, as Harper’s quest to find her son pushes her to the very edge of reason.</p> <p><b>This original podcast is 10 episodes in total, please begin with “Ep 1: Vanished”.</b></p>"; 
